spec: agent-core.ai-docs/v1
namespace: "Contract\\Extension"
fqcn: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Contract\\Extension"
updatedAt: 2026-04-22
description: "Extension seam interfaces for third-party integrations — command handlers, event subscribers, hook subscribers."
files[3]{file,type,summary}:
  CommandHandlerInterface.php,interface,"Handles extension commands with kind-based dispatch, validation, and payload mapping."
  EventSubscriberInterface.php,interface,Reacts to specific domain events by declaring subscribed event types and processing them.
  HookSubscriberInterface.php,interface,Subscribes to named hooks and processes incoming hook events with context data.